revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{Lua|Module:Category pair}}
<!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE -->

==Usage==
* {{tlx|Succeeding category|CATEGORY NAME}}

Enter the ''category name only'' of the target category, leaving out the term "Category:". 

==Example==
* {{tlx|Succeeding category|21st century by continent}} &rarr; {{Succeeding category|21st century by continent}}

Non-existent categories return empty

* {{tlx|Succeeding category|57th century by continent}} &rarr; {{Succeeding category|57th century by continent}}

==See also==
* {{tl|Preceding category}}
* {{tl|Category pair}}

{{Category hatnote templates}}

<includeonly>{{sandbox other||
[[Category:Internal category-link templates]]
[[Category:Hatnote templates for category pages]]
}}
</includeonly>

